The circuit to be built:

Smart Dog Harness - System Block Diagram
========================================

    ┌─────────────────┐
    │   Arduino Uno   │
    │  (Main MCU)     │
    └─────────┬───────┘
              │
    ┌─────────┼──────────────────────────────┐
    │         │                              │
    │    ┌────▼────┐  ┌──────────┐  ┌────────▼─────┐
    │    │ NEO-6M  │  │ SIM800C  │  │ Pulse Sensor │
    │    │   GPS   │  │   GSM    │  │   (A0 Pin)   │
    │    │(Pin 8,9)│  │(Pin 2,3) │  └──────────────┘
    │    └─────────┘  └──────────┘           │
    │                                        │
    │    ┌─────────┐   ┌──────────┐          │
    └────┤HC-05 BT │   │Push Btn  │──────────┘
         │Module   │   │(Pin 4)   │
         └─────────┘   └──────────┘

Data Flow:
GPS → Location Tracking → Geofencing Algorithm
Pulse Sensor → Heart Rate → Health Monitoring  
GSM → SMS Alerts → Emergency Communication
Button → Emergency Call → Direct Communication
Bluetooth → Data Transfer → Mobile App


Make it compact and fit it into a stitched pocket in your dog harness with a tiny hole for the call button to stick out
